== World Electric Vehicle Association (WEVA) ==
[[Electric Drive Transportation Association]], with EVAAP (Electric Vehicle Association of Asia Pacific)<ref>http://www.evaap.org/ </ref> and AVERE <ref> http://www.avere.org/</ref>, form  the World Electric Vehicle Association (WEVA). 

Its [[chairman]] is Hisashi Ishitani.

